\ Functional words over arrays: find / any? / all? / each / flat-map /
\ sort-by / partition / group-with.

\ === find ==================================================================
[ 1 2 3 4 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] find . cr             \ 2   (first match, not 4)
[ 1 3 5 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] find . cr               \ null
[ ] [: drop 1 :] find . cr                       \ null
[ "a" "bb" "ccc" ] [: size 2 = :] find . cr      \ bb

\ === any? / all? ===========================================================
[ 1 3 5 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] any? . cr               \ 0
[ 1 2 3 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] any? . cr               \ 1
[ ] [: drop 1 :] any? . cr                       \ 0
[ 2 4 6 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] all? . cr               \ 1
[ 2 4 5 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] all? . cr               \ 0
[ ] [: drop 0 :] all? . cr                       \ 1   (vacuously true)

\ === each ==================================================================
0 to total
[ 1 2 3 4 ] [: total + to total :] each
total . cr                                       \ 10
[ ] [: total + to total :] each
total . cr                                       \ 10  (no elements, no calls)

\ === flat-map ==============================================================
[ 1 2 3 ] [: dup 2 array :] flat-map . cr        \ [ 1 1 2 2 3 3 ]
[ 1 2 3 ] [: drop [ ] :] flat-map . cr           \ [ ]
[ 1 3 ] [: dup 1 + range :] flat-map . cr        \ [ 1 2 3 4 ]

\ === sort-by ===============================================================
[ "ccc" "a" "bb" ] [: size :] sort-by . cr       \ [ "a" "bb" "ccc" ]
[ 3 1 4 1 5 9 2 6 ] [: negate :] sort-by . cr    \ descending
[ ] [: negate :] sort-by . cr                    \ [ ]
[ { :n 2 } { :n 1 } ] [: :n @ :] sort-by . cr    \ frames by field

\ === partition =============================================================
[ 1 2 3 4 5 6 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] partition swap . . cr   \ evens then odds
[ 1 3 5 ] [: 2 mod 0= :] partition swap . . cr         \ [ ] then all
[ ] [: drop 1 :] partition swap . . cr                 \ both empty

\ === group-with ============================================================
[ 1 2 3 4 5 ] [: 2 mod 0= if :even else :odd then :] group-with . cr
[ ] [: drop :x :] group-with . cr                \ { }
[ "ant" "bee" "cow" "asp" ] [: 0 1 substring string>symbol :] group-with . cr

\ === exit inside a bare quotation ends the iteration ======================
\ (the direct-dispatch loop path: exit stops at the run floor, no frame)
[ 1 2 3 ] [: dup 2 = if drop 99 exit then 1+ :] map . cr   \ [ 2 99 4 ]
[: 7 :] 2 times . . cr                                     \ 7 7
[ 1 2 3 ] [| x | to x x 2 = if 0 exit then x :] map . cr   \ [ 1 0 3 ] scratch frame

bye
